name: Cube Runner (itch) (theasian_baller)
description:
I present to you all Cube Runner, my very first 3D game. Simplistic yet challenging, with 30 levels to complete! Think you can dodge and wave your way through the block field and make it to the end of all 30 levels?

*Please note that at the time of finishing this, I, as well as those who helped on making this game, will be in high school, so please do not judge too harshly*
